{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1435980/extras/Sloth-Tales-dash-narrow.gif?t=1733824461\" /><br>Jimmy the Sloth embarks on his own magical adventure. Think Lion Quest, but with a sloth.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Sloth Tales delights and inspires with the following features:</h2><br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1435980/extras/Sloth-Tales-underwater-narrow.gif?t=1733824461\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A mighty-fine and very free platforming adventure. Where you play as Jimmy the Sloth.</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1435980/extras/Sloth-Tales-portal.gif?t=1733824461\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Dash and high-jump powerups redefine play with new ways to explore.<br></li><li>A light amount of story \u2013 just enough to leave you wanting more!</li></ul><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1435980/extras/Sloth-Tales-main.gif?t=1733824461\" /><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Open-ended design where the levels can be played through in any order. Plus a small amount of randomness ensures no two Sloth Tales are exactly the same.<br></li><li>Soundtrack is a brand-new song by the band Falcon Ave. \u2013 perhaps their catchiest one yet.</li></ul><br>\u2013\u2013\u2013\u2013<br><br>Approx. playtime 30 mins (maybe 1hr if you take your time)<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1435980/extras/Sloth.png?t=1733824461\" /><br><br>Sloth Tales is a standalone adventure, but it's also part of the even-more amazing game Lion Quest Infinity, which is also available on Steam.","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Roy the Pig","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1435980/ab85a7a4ed7ec136060e3